alamusNX\":\"56.8\",\"BrainRNAMidbrainNX\":\"48.5\",\"BrainRNAOlfactoryRegionNX\":\"33.9\",\"BrainRNAPonsAndMedullaNX\":\"55.7\",\"BrainRNAThalamusNX\":\"24.8\"}',NULL,'The protein encoded by this gene is a small GTPase of the Rho-subfamily, which regulates signaling pathways that control diverse cellular functions including cell morphology, migration, endocytosis and cell cycle progression. This protein is highly similar to Saccharomyces cerevisiae Cdc 42, and is able to complement the yeast cdc42-1 mutant. The product of oncogene Dbl was reported to specifically catalyze the dissociation of GDP from this protein. This protein could regulate actin polymerization through its direct binding to Neural Wiskott-Aldrich syndrome protein (N-WASP), which subsequently activates Arp2/3 complex. Alternative splicing of this gene results in multiple transcript variants. Pseudogenes of this gene have been identified on chromosomes 3, 4, 5, 7, 8 and 20. [provided by RefSeq, Apr 2013]');
INSERT INTO `gene` VALUES (250,'ARNTL','MOP3 JAP3 BMAL1 PASD3 bHLHe5','aryl hydrocarbon receptor nuclear translocator-like',406,'BMAL1_HUMAN','mammal','11p15',13277727,13387265,1,'','NM_001178','NP_001169','1,678,796,016,847,340,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000','Arntl;Mus musculus,Arntl;Rattus norvegicus,cyc;Drosophila melanogaster,arntl1a;Danio rerio,arntl1b;Danio rerio','Входят в состав \"молекулярных часов\". Ортологи насекомых оразуют одельный кластер, гомологи позвоночных формируют отдельный кластер. Отрологи имеют сходие функции [1, 2].','Активатор транскрипции, который формирует центральный компонент \"молекулярных\" часов [3]. Формирует гетеродимер с CLOCK протеином, имеет сайт связывания с ДНК [4].','Прямые доказательства на млекопитающих, Прямые доказательства на культурах клеток','Дефицит ARNTL у мышей и в человеческих клеточных линиях приводит к раннему старению и связанными со старением патологиями. Срок жизни мышей сократился с 52 до 37 недель [5] [6]. [5] 10.1101/gad.1432206, [6] 10.18632/aging.100633','Part of \'clock\' genes. insect orthologs cluster separately, while the Vertebrata sequences fall into different paralogous [1, 2].','Transcriptional activator which forms a core component of the circadian clock [3]. Forms heterodimers with CLOCK protein, has DNA recognition site [4].','Mice deficient in ARNTL1 (BMAL1) are developing early aging and age-related pathologies. Lifespan decreased from 52 to 37 weeks [5]. Same results are shown in human cell lines [5] [6].','[1] 10.1177/0748730404268775, [2] 10.1177/0748730402238232, [3] https://www.uniprot.org/uniprot/O00327, [4] 10.1038/cr.2012.170',NULL,1,0,NULL,1614619505,3,'','',2,'ENSG00000133794','{\"Gene\":\"ARNTL\",\"GeneSynonym\":[\"bHLHe5\",\"BMAL1\",\"JAP3\",\"MOP3\",\"PASD3\"],\"Ensembl\":\"ENSG00000133794\",\"GeneDescription\":\"Aryl hydrocarbon receptor nuclear translocator like\",\"Uniprot\":[\"O0