atterns. Several transcript variants encoding different isoforms have been found for this gene. [provided by RefSeq, Jul 2014]');
INSERT INTO `gene` VALUES (251,'CLOCK','KIAA0334 KAT13D bHLHe8','clock circadian regulator',9575,'CLOCK_HUMAN','functional,downstream','4q12',55427901,55546909,-1,'','NM_004898','NP_004889','16,787,960,168,473,400,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000,000','Clock;Mus musculus,clocka;Danio rerio,Clk;Drosophila melanogaster,Clock;Rattus norvegicus,clockb;Danio rerio','Циркадная система прошла через генетическую революцию в кембрийскую эру. У насекомых гены связанные с циркадными ритмами присутствуют в одной копии, а у позвоночных они дуплицированы [1].','Ключевой регулятор транскрипции генов, связанный с работой циркадных часов. Выполняет основную регуляцию экспрессии генов в течение суток [2, 3]. Фактор транскрипции CLOCK образует гетеродимер с BMAL1 для связывания с E-box мотивом генов -мишеней CLOCK[4].','Прямые доказательства на млекопитающих','Аутофагия и циркадные часы препятствуют дегенерации тканей и поддерживают долголетие у многих организмов [5]. Недостаток CLOCK у мышей сокращает продолжительность жизни на 15–20 процентов по сравнению с диким типом [6].','The circadian system was also carried along with this genetic revolution, and so clock and clock-related genes that are found in a single copy in insects are duplicated in vertebrates [1].','Transcriptional activator which forms a core component of the circadian clock. Executes the main diurnal expression regulation [2, 3]. The core transcription factors CLOCK and BMAL1 heterodimerize and bind to E-box motif-containing clock-controlled genes [4].','Autophagy and the circadian clock counteract tissue degeneration and support longevity in many organisms [5]. Deficiency of the CLOCK protein significantly affects longevity: the average lifespan of Clock-/- mice is reduced by 15–20 percent compared with wild type mice [6].','[1] 10.1177/0748730404268775, [2] 10.1111/j.1538-7836.2012.04643.x., [3] 10.1007/s11010-008-9846-x, [4] 10.1007/s13238-016-0366-2, [5] 10.18632/aging.101018, [6] 10.18632/aging.100241',NULL,1,0,NULL,1614756630,3,'','',6,'ENSG00000134852','{\"Gene\":\"CLOCK\",\"GeneSynonym\":[\"bHLHe8\",\"KAT13D\",\"KIAA0334\"],\"Ensembl\":\"ENSG00000134852\",\"GeneDescription\":\"Clock circadian regulator\",\"Uniprot\":[\"O15516\"],\"Chromosome\":\"4\",\"Position\":\"55427903-55547138\",\"ProteinClass\":[\"Enzymes\",\"Predicted intracellular proteins\",\"Transcription factors\"],\"BiologicalProcess\":[\"Biological rhythms\",\"DNA damage\",\"Transcription\",\"Transcription regulation\"],\"MolecularFunction\":[\"Activator\",\"Acyltransferase\",\"DNA-binding\",\"Transferase\"],\"DiseaseInvolvement\":null,\"Evidence\":\"Evidence at protein level\",\"HPAEvidence\":\"Evidence at protein level\",\"UniProtEvidence\":\"Evidence at protein level\",\"NeXtProtEvidence\":\"Evidence at protein level\",\"MSEvidence\":\"Evidence at protein level\",\"RNATissueSpecificity\":\"Low tissue specificity\",\"RNATissueDistribution\":\"Detected in all\",\"RNATissueSpecificityScore\":null,\"RNATissueSpecificNX\":null,\"RNACellLineSpecificity\":\"Low cell line specificity\",\"RNACellLineDistribution\":\"Detected in all\",\"RNACellLineSpecificityScore\":null,\"RNACellLineSpecificNX\":null,\"RNACancerSpecificity\":\"Low cancer specificity\",\"RNACancerDistribution\":\"Detected in all\",\"RNACancerSpecificityScore\":null,\"RNACancerSpecificFPKM\":null,\"RNABrainRegionalSpecificity\":\"Low region specificity\",\"RNABrainRegionalDistribution\":\"Detected in all\",\"RNABrainRegionalSpecificityScore\":null,\"RNABrainRegionalSpecificNX\":null,\"RNABloodCellSpecificity\":\"Low cell type specificity\",\"RNABloodCellDistribution\":\"Detected in many\",\"RNABloodCellSpecificityScore\":null,\"RNABloodCellSpecificNX\":null,\"RNABloodLineageSpecificity\":\"Low lineage specificity\",\"RNABloodLineageDistribution\":\"Detected in many\",\"RNABloodLineageSpecificityScore\":null,\"RNABloodLi